 Details

Project Name: Palindrome Checker GUI  
Version: 1.0  
Author: [MD Riad Khan]  
Email: [mdriyadkhan585@gmail.com]  
Website: [https://rkstudio.com]

Description:
The Palindrome Checker GUI is a Python application with a graphical user interface built using PySide6. It allows users to check if a string is a palindrome and provides functionality for theme switching and exiting the application. This software is provided under the MIT License, allowing for both personal and commercial use with minimal restrictions.

